INKANTOLO enkulu eGauteng isichithile isinqumo esamenyezelwa nguNgqongqoshe wezeMfundo kuleli uNkk Angie Motshekga sokuthi kuphinde kubhalwe amaphepha ka-matric aputshuka. Ijaji uNorman Davis lithe lesi sinqumo asihambisani nemigomo, asikho emthethweni futhi kumele sibuyekezwe ngakho uyasichitha. Umnyango ubuphakamise ukuthi lawa maphepha okuyiphepha lesibili leMaths, nephepha lesibili leSayensi, kumele abhalwe kabusha ngesonto elizayo. I-Afriforum, iSadtu nezinye izinhlangano zifake udaba enkantolo ziphikisa isinqumo somnyango. Ijaji lithe abafundi banelungelo lokuthi amakwe amaphepha abawabhalile bese kuba kuMnyango ukuthi wenzani ngabafundi okuzotholwa ukuthi baphule umthetho. Umnyango uyalelwe ukuthi ukhokhele izindleko zecala.